newsitem.title: USA: Iowa-S Minn cattle market not well tested - USDA.
newsitem.headline: Iowa-S Minn cattle market not well tested - USDA.

text.p: Steers and heifers were not tested, compared with Thursday's close, USDA said.
Carcass basis Steers and heifers also not well tested.
